node.title: All the latest coronavirus news you need to know today
node.description: Get up to speed on all the COVID-19 updates from across Australia. Follow live.
node.content: ["Northern Territory health authorities are waiting for the results of 20 \"priority tests\" from the small community of Robinson River,\u00a0where one of Monday's two new cases tested positive, triggering a snap lockdown.\u00a0", "Follow all of Wednesday's news and updates on our live blog."]
